fields.title: Clean my cat
fields.description: Please, I need help cleaning my cat. He tried to go number 2 in the litter but the poop stuck to him and it went all over his fur.

fields.title: Lost Dog
fields.description: Please, our family dog got out last night after the fourth of july fireworks scared him away. We've been looking for him ever since. He's a german shepeard with a blue collar and one limp ear.

fields.title: Ipad for sale
fields.description: I've been using this ipad for a while so I thought it was time for an upgrade so I'm selling this for cheap.

fields.title: I'll clean your yard
fields.description: I do a side business for yard clean-ups and upkeeps. If anyone is in need of lawn care and maintenance I'm your guy.

fields.title: Rental Space Available
fields.description: I have recently vacated a swamp with a nice shoreside housing. It's fully furnished and is ready for a new owner. NOTE: it does have some wildlife nearby.
